,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"當時冇咁高科技，啲人點會好似現代人咁冇得上網就悶<br />\n<br />\n而且古代啲人工作大多數都係耕田(應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，耕得嚟都冇咗半日，剩番啲時間一係約朋友飲酒吹水，一係就準備餸菜煮飯，劈柴，湊仔女咁<br />\n<br />\n讀書人，睇書，約朋友遊山玩水，作詩，溫科舉，去青樓叫雞，咁多嘢做點會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83d77b7a6bf925122539c162eb0806b16e76251","tid":772363,"uid":179340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:20:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7036c3f63922e87f9b42c44bd470ffbbb7b7a0d3","tid":772363,"uid":138762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"古代人冇冷氣係點生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d528b959dc313adf601e98cf07953f4e6eb3ed38","tid":772363,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:28:23.000Z","msg":"以前好多人淨係為生存已經用盡精力, 邊得閒諗悶唔悶<br />\n悶係一種奢侈"},{"pid":"ed953e94825132012a3031785dc55292e516debe","tid":772363,"uid":87573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"係，所以死晒"},{"pid":"a2c4a1620e33442be5014dd82236557f7d89acea","tid":772363,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:29:52.000Z","msg":"所以大把時間出街溝女"},{"pid":"14ce7b69534e395b8e5253696761645e17ff45fe","tid":772363,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"空想, 連悶既感覺都消失.."},{"pid":"568eb9dcad2a4d54ad80f4603595cb74bb042a81","tid":772363,"uid":171555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"你人生得返上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e598c67c537979c2d9da8d24087044b132f0067","tid":772363,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6b854ab2750d229be092c9547b3c35c363268ff","tid":772363,"uid":84524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:19:51.000Z","msg":"當時冇咁高科技，啲人點會好似現代人咁冇得上網就悶<br />\n<br />\n而且古代啲人工作大多數都係耕田(應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，耕得嚟都冇咗半日，剩番啲時間一係約朋友飲酒吹水，一係就準備餸菜煮飯，劈柴，湊仔女咁<br />\n<br />\n讀書人，睇書，約朋友遊山玩水，作詩，溫科舉，去青樓叫雞，咁多嘢做點會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:11:54.000Z","msg":"廿年前都唔係家家戶戶都有上網啦，唔洗講咁遠ge。以前細個冇上網咪睇電視落街玩囉，大人都係睇報紙睇電視。放假想去行商場，食下野又一日。宜家個個上網先冇乜人睇電視睇報紙，成個商場都係蝗先冇乜人行遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3fa8cfb5e5c304016502d2eae2cb81376137e7","tid":772363,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"睇電視、報紙、書，聽電台、出街行。<br />\n<br />\n所以現時傳統傳媒已半死。"},{"pid":"3df675b02a9700daceac1b5cb67ebd247f11f7d6","tid":772363,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"睇書"},{"pid":"9dc4515f76ebcd2eb81c5d993e9baffbf6c64ad6","tid":772363,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"古時上青樓尋歡大約咩價位"},{"pid":"c17993b8ff6052b2c87a8b8fec39ec333001ea18","tid":772363,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dc4515f76ebcd2eb81c5d993e9baffbf6c64ad6","tid":772363,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"古時上青樓尋歡大約咩價位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"要睇你想玩乜女同要乜嘢服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}